Package: ftExtra
Title: Extensions for Flextable
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Atsushi Yasumoto [aut, cph, cre] (<https://orcid.org/0000-0002-8335-495X>)
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Atsushi",
