           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8335-495X"))
Maintainer: Atsushi Yasumoto <atusy.rpkg@gmail.com>
URL: https://github.com/atusy/ftExtra
BugReports: https://github.com/atusy/ftExtra/issues
Description:
    Build display tables easily by extending the functionality of the flextable package.
    Features include spanning headers, grouping rows, parsing markdown texts and so on.
